        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for sending Moritz Wagner’s letter and his essays [on "Der Naturprocess der Artbildung" in <hi rend="italic">Das Ausland</hi> (1875)]. Will read them and write to Wagner when his health is better.</p> 
            <p>Declines to receive Scherzer at Down.</p>
